Interface IInitMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMessage, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface IInitMessage
extends IMessage
    A message only sent outside chatroom. Well-known "initial" messages are: Invitation2Chatroom, ChatroomListRequest, ChatroomListResponse, InitUserInfoRequest, InitUserInfoResponse.
